            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;">&nbsp;</p>
            </span><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;"><strong>Significado</strong></p>
            </span></span></span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td width="146" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 109.35pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1pt; border-left-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Em processamento</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td width="428" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 321.25pt; border-style: none solid solid none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A declara&ccedil;&atilde;o foi recebida, mas o processamento ainda n&atilde;o foi conclu&iacute;do.</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td width="146" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 109.35pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1pt; border-left-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Em Fila de Restitui&ccedil;&atilde;o</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td width="428" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 321.25pt; border-style: none solid solid none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Indica que, ap&oacute;s o processamento da declara&ccedil;&atilde;o, o contribuinte tem direito a restitui&ccedil;&atilde;o, mas que ainda n&atilde;o foi disponibilizada na rede banc&aacute;ria.<br />
            Para recebimento da restitui&ccedil;&atilde;o, o contribuinte n&atilde;o poder&aacute; ter pend&ecirc;ncias de d&eacute;bitos no &acirc;mbito da RFB e/ou da PGFN.</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td width="146" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 109.35pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1pt; border-left-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Processada</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td width="428" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 321.25pt; border-style: none solid solid none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">A declara&ccedil;&atilde;o foi recebida e o seu processamento conclu&iacute;do.<br />
            Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o: A situa&ccedil;&atilde;o &ldquo;processada&rdquo; n&atilde;o significa que o resultado apurado tenha sido homologado, podendo ser revisto de of&iacute;cio pela Administra&ccedil;&atilde;o Tribut&aacute;ria (artigo 150, &sect; 4&ordm;, do C&oacute;digo Tribut&aacute;rio Nacional &ndash; CTN).</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td width="146" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 109.35pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1pt; border-left-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Com Pend&ecirc;ncias</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td width="428" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 321.25pt; border-style: none solid solid none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Durante o processamento da declara&ccedil;&atilde;o foram encontradas pend&ecirc;ncias em rela&ccedil;&atilde;o a algumas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es. O contribuinte deve regularizar as pend&ecirc;ncias.</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td width="146" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 109.35pt; border-style: none solid solid; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-left-width: 1pt; border-left-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Em An&aacute;lise</span></span></span></p>
            </td>
            <td width="428" style="font-family: arial, sans-serif; margin: 0px; width: 321.25pt; border-style: none solid solid none; border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: windowtext; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: windowtext; padding: 0pt 4pt;">
            <p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0px; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 22px; padding-bottom: 20px; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="font-family: Arial;"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Indica que a declara&ccedil;&atilde;o foi recepcionada, encontra-se na base de dados da Receita Federal do Brasil e aguarda: a) a apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o de documentos solicitados em intima&ccedil;&atilde;o enviada ao contribuinte; ou<br />
            b) a conclus&atilde;o da an&aacute;lise de documentos entregues pelo contribuinte por meio de agendamento, em atendimento &agrave; intima&ccedil;&atilde;o a ele enviada, ou para apresentar Solicita&ccedil;&atilde;o de Retifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de Lan&ccedil;amento (SRL).</span></span></span></p>
